Description:
To reach the obelisk you have to cross a pond of water, when you approach you see something moving underneath.

Suddenly four snake-shaped heads appear, it's a hydra! Each head looks a little different from the rest and you take some time to name them according to their characteristics.

Since it doesn't move, you can decide how to position yourselves and which head you want to fight first at the front.
DescriptionAction: If you do not attack immediately, the hydra will have time to prepare.
